Dear fibonacci.vic,

Do fibonacci(n) {
    Madame a = 0
    Madame b = 1
    Madame count = 0

    Whilst (count < n) persists {
        Inscribe(a)

        Madame next = a + b
        a = b
        b = next

        count = count + 1
    }

    Hasten back a
}

Do commence() {
    Madame limit = 10
    fibonacci(limit)
}

